      <title>暑期研0居家学习笔记：从五个练习理解 NumPy</title>
      <link href="/2026/07/08/Python/numpy_five_exercises_blog_summary/"/>
      <url>/2026/07/08/Python/numpy_five_exercises_blog_summary/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1>暑期研0居家学习笔记：从五个练习理解 NumPy</h1><p>这组 NumPy 练习看起来只是五段代码：z-score 标准化、余弦相似度矩阵、Softmax、One-Hot 编码和 k-NN 距离矩阵。写完以后我发现，真正值得记住的不是某一行 API，而是 NumPy 处理问题的方式。</p><p>简单说，就是先想清楚数组形状，再决定沿哪个维度计算。只要形状对了，很多原本想用循环解决的问题，都可以变成广播、索引或者矩阵乘法。</p><p>这篇文章按五个练习整理一下这套思路。</p><h2 id="练习一：z-score-标准化">练习一：z-score 标准化</h2><h3 id="任务">任务</h3><p>给定一个形状为 <code>(100, 5)</code> 的数据矩阵，对每一列做 z-score 标准化，让每一列的均值接近 0，标准差接近 1。</p><h3 id="代码">代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">data = np.random.randn(<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">data_normalized = (</span><br><span class="line">    data - np.mean(data, axis=<span class="number">0</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">) / np.std(data, axis=<span class="number">0</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> np.allclose(np.mean(data_normalized, axis=<span class="number">0</span>), <span class="number">0</span>) <span class="keyword">and</span> np.allclose(np.std(data_normalized, axis=<span class="number">0</span>), <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;Data is successfully normalized.&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心逻辑">核心逻辑</h3><p><code>axis=0</code> 表示沿着行方向聚合，也就是对每一列分别计算均值和标准差。</p><p>原始数据形状是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">data.shape  <span class="comment"># (100, 5)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果不加 <code>keepdims=True</code>，列均值的形状是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.mean(data, axis=<span class="number">0</span>).shape  <span class="comment"># (5,)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>加上 <code>keepdims=True</code> 后，形状变成：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.mean(data, axis=<span class="number">0</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>).shape  <span class="comment"># (1, 5)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样后面的广播会更直观：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">5</span>) - (<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">5</span>) -&gt; (<span class="number">100</span>, <span class="number">5</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里 <code>(1, 5)</code> 会在第一维自动广播成 <code>(100, 5)</code>，于是每一列都会减去自己的均值。</p><h3 id="为什么用-np-allclose">为什么用 <code>np.allclose</code></h3><p>标准化后的均值理论上应该是 0，但浮点数计算会有很小的误差，比如 <code>1e-16</code>。所以不能直接写 <code>== 0</code>，更合适的是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.allclose(np.mean(data_normalized, axis=<span class="number">0</span>), <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这也是数值计算里一个很常见的习惯：判断相等时，很多时候判断的是足够接近。</p><h2 id="练习二：余弦相似度矩阵">练习二：余弦相似度矩阵</h2><h3 id="任务-2">任务</h3><p>给定形状为 <code>(10, 128)</code> 的矩阵 <code>A</code>，其中每一行是一个 128 维向量。现在要计算 10 个向量两两之间的余弦相似度，输出形状为 <code>(10, 10)</code> 的矩阵。</p><h3 id="代码-2">代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">A = np.random.randn(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">128</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">A_norm = A / np.sqrt(np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(A ** <span class="number">2</span>, axis=<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">similarity = A_norm @ A_norm.T</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心逻辑-2">核心逻辑</h3><p>余弦相似度公式是：</p><p>$$\cos(x, y) = \frac{x \cdot y}{|x||y|}$$</p><p>如果先把每个向量都做 L2 归一化，让每个向量的长度变成 1，那么余弦相似度就可以直接写成点积：</p><p>$$\cos(x, y) = x_{\text{norm}} \cdot y_{\text{norm}}$$</p><p>关键是先计算每一行的 L2 范数：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.sqrt(np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(A ** <span class="number">2</span>, axis=<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里有三个点：</p><ul><li><code>A ** 2</code> 是元素级平方，不是矩阵乘法；</li><li><code>axis=1</code> 表示沿每一行的特征维度求和；</li><li><code>keepdims=True</code> 让范数形状保持为 <code>(10, 1)</code>。</li></ul><p>所以归一化时的形状变化是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">128</span>) / (<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">1</span>) -&gt; (<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">128</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后用矩阵乘法：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">A_norm @ A_norm.T</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>形状变化为：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">128</span>) @ (<span class="number">128</span>, <span class="number">10</span>) -&gt; (<span class="number">10</span>, <span class="number">10</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这一步一次性算出了所有向量两两之间的点积，比写双重 <code>for</code> 循环清爽很多。</p><h2 id="练习三：数值稳定版-Softmax">练习三：数值稳定版 Softmax</h2><h3 id="任务-3">任务</h3><p>实现一个可以处理任意批次维度 <code>(..., C)</code> 的 Softmax 函数，并且在最后一维上计算概率分布。</p><h3 id="代码-3">代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">softmax</span>(<span class="params">x</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    x_max = np.<span class="built_in">max</span>(x, axis=-<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    exp_x = np.exp(x - x_max)</span><br><span class="line">    sum_exp_x = np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(exp_x, axis=-<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> exp_x / sum_exp_x</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心逻辑-3">核心逻辑</h3><p>Softmax 的原始形式是：</p><p>$$\text{softmax}(x_i) = \frac{e^{x_i}}{\sum_j e^{x_j}}$$</p><p>如果直接计算 <code>np.exp(x)</code>，当输入很大时会溢出。比如 <code>np.exp(1000)</code> 会变成无穷大，后面再除就很容易得到 <code>NaN</code>。</p><p>更稳的写法是先减去最后一维的最大值：</p><p>$$\text{softmax}(x_i) = \frac{e^{x_i - \max(x)}}{\sum_j e^{x_j - \max(x)}}$$</p><p>这个变换在数学上等价，因为分子和分母同时乘了同一个常数因子，最终比例不变。</p><p>在代码里：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x_max = np.<span class="built_in">max</span>(x, axis=-<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>axis=-1</code> 表示始终沿最后一维计算。这比写死 <code>axis=1</code> 更通用，因为输入可能是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(batch, classes)</span><br><span class="line">(batch, time, classes)</span><br><span class="line">(batch, height, width, channels)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>只要类别维或者特征维在最后一维，<code>axis=-1</code> 就能工作。</p><p><code>keepdims=True</code> 仍然是为了让广播稳定：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">x.shape      <span class="comment"># (..., C)</span></span><br><span class="line">x_max.shape  <span class="comment"># (..., 1)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这样 <code>x - x_max</code> 就能自然广播，结果仍然保持原始输入的形状。</p><h2 id="练习四：One-Hot-编码">练习四：One-Hot 编码</h2><h3 id="任务-4">任务</h3><p>实现 <code>one_hot(labels, num_classes)</code>。其中 <code>labels</code> 的形状为 <code>(N,)</code>，返回形状为 <code>(N, num_classes)</code> 的 <code>float32</code> 矩阵。</p><h3 id="代码-4">代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">one_hot</span>(<span class="params">labels, num_classes</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> np.eye(num_classes, dtype=np.float32)[labels]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心逻辑-4">核心逻辑</h3><p><code>np.eye(num_classes)</code> 会生成一个单位矩阵。例如：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.eye(<span class="number">4</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>得到：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">array([</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">1.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">1.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">1.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">1.</span>]</span><br><span class="line">])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个单位矩阵可以看成一个类别模板库：</p><ul><li>第 0 行表示类别 0 的 one-hot 编码；</li><li>第 1 行表示类别 1 的 one-hot 编码；</li><li>第 2 行表示类别 2 的 one-hot 编码；</li><li>第 3 行表示类别 3 的 one-hot 编码。</li></ul><p>如果：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">labels = np.array([<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span>, <span class="number">1</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>那么：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.eye(<span class="number">4</span>, dtype=np.float32)[labels]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>等价于按顺序取出第 2 行、第 0 行、第 1 行，结果是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">array([</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">1.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">1.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">1.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>, <span class="number">0.</span>]</span><br><span class="line">], dtype=np.float32)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里用到的是 NumPy 的高级索引。它不是逐个写循环，而是直接用标签数组批量索引单位矩阵的行。</p><h2 id="练习五：向量化实现-k-NN-距离矩阵">练习五：向量化实现 k-NN 距离矩阵</h2><h3 id="任务-5">任务</h3><p>实现 <code>knn_distances(query, database)</code>，不使用 <code>for</code> 循环，一次性计算 <code>Q</code> 个查询向量和 <code>N</code> 个数据库向量之间的欧氏距离。</p><p>输入形状：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">query.shape     <span class="comment"># (Q, D)</span></span><br><span class="line">database.shape  <span class="comment"># (N, D)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出形状：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">distances.shape <span class="comment"># (Q, N)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="代码-5">代码</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> numpy <span class="keyword">as</span> np</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">knn_distances</span>(<span class="params">query, database</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    query_3d = query[:, np.newaxis, :]       <span class="comment"># (Q, D) -&gt; (Q, 1, D)</span></span><br><span class="line">    database_3d = database[np.newaxis, :, :] <span class="comment"># (N, D) -&gt; (1, N, D)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    diff = query_3d - database_3d            <span class="comment"># (Q, N, D)</span></span><br><span class="line">    distances = np.sqrt(np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(diff ** <span class="number">2</span>, axis=-<span class="number">1</span>))</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> distances</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="核心逻辑-5">核心逻辑</h3><p>欧氏距离公式是：</p><p>$$d(x, y) = \sqrt{\sum_{k=1}^{D}(x_k - y_k)^2}$$</p><p>如果直接写循环，通常会写成：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(Q):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(N):</span><br><span class="line">        compute_distance(query[i], database[j])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>NumPy 的做法是先通过升维制造广播条件：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">query[:, np.newaxis, :]       <span class="comment"># (Q, D) -&gt; (Q, 1, D)</span></span><br><span class="line">database[np.newaxis, :, :]    <span class="comment"># (N, D) -&gt; (1, N, D)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后广播相减：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(Q, <span class="number">1</span>, D) - (<span class="number">1</span>, N, D) -&gt; (Q, N, D)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>得到的 <code>diff[i, j, :]</code>，就是第 <code>i</code> 个 query 向量和第 <code>j</code> 个 database 向量在所有特征维度上的差值。</p><p>接下来沿最后一维求平方和：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(diff ** <span class="number">2</span>, axis=-<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>形状从：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(Q, N, D) -&gt; (Q, N)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最后开方得到距离矩阵。</p><h3 id="大数据场景下的改进">大数据场景下的改进</h3><p>广播版本很适合理解机制，但它会创建一个形状为 <code>(Q, N, D)</code> 的三维中间数组。如果 <code>Q</code>、<code>N</code>、<code>D</code> 都很大，内存压力会很高。</p><p>更适合大规模数据的做法是使用平方展开：</p><p>$$|u - v|^2 = |u|^2 + |v|^2 - 2uv^T$$</p><p>代码是：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">knn_distances_fast</span>(<span class="params">query, database</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    query_sq = np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(query ** <span class="number">2</span>, axis=<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>)         <span class="comment"># (Q, 1)</span></span><br><span class="line">    database_sq = np.<span class="built_in">sum</span>(database ** <span class="number">2</span>, axis=<span class="number">1</span>, keepdims=<span class="literal">True</span>).T <span class="comment"># (1, N)</span></span><br><span class="line">    cross = query @ database.T                                  <span class="comment"># (Q, N)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    distances_sq = query_sq + database_sq - <span class="number">2</span> * cross</span><br><span class="line">    distances_sq = np.maximum(distances_sq, <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> np.sqrt(distances_sq)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个版本不需要构造 <code>(Q, N, D)</code>，而是直接得到 <code>(Q, N)</code> 的距离矩阵，更接近实际工程中的写法。</p><h2 id="总结：五道题串起来的主线">总结：五道题串起来的主线</h2><p>这五个练习可以看成 NumPy 学习的一个小闭环。</p><p>第一题 z-score 标准化，解决的是如何沿某个维度做统计，并把统计量广播回原数组。这里的重点是 <code>axis</code>、<code>keepdims=True</code> 和广播。</p><p>第二题余弦相似度矩阵，解决的是如何把一组向量之间的两两关系转成矩阵乘法。这里的重点是 L2 归一化、转置和矩阵乘法。</p><p>第三题 Softmax，解决的是如何写出既通用又数值稳定的函数。这里的重点是 <code>axis=-1</code>、减最大值和避免指数上溢出。</p><p>第四题 One-Hot 编码，解决的是如何用高级索引替代手写循环。这里的重点是把单位矩阵看成类别模板库，再用标签数组批量取行。</p><p>第五题 k-NN 距离矩阵，解决的是如何通过升维和广播一次性计算所有两两组合。这里的重点是 <code>np.newaxis</code>、三维广播和沿最后一维聚合。</p><p>它们最后都指向同一个能力：不要只把数组看成一堆数字，要先看它的形状。形状设计清楚以后，很多看似需要循环的问题，都可以转化成一次广播、一次索引或者一次矩阵乘法。</p><h2 id="我对-NumPy-的理解变化">我对 NumPy 的理解变化</h2><p>刚开始写 NumPy 时，我很容易把注意力放在单个函数名上，比如 <code>mean</code>、<code>sum</code>、<code>dot</code>、<code>exp</code>。但写完这几个练习以后会发现，函数名本身不是最难的，难的是知道它在哪个维度上算，算完以后形状怎么变，后面还能不能继续广播。</p><p>现在我会按这个顺序检查：</p><ol><li>先写出输入数组的形状；</li><li>判断要在哪个 <code>axis</code> 上计算；</li><li>判断聚合后是否需要 <code>keepdims=True</code>；</li><li>检查广播时各维度能否从右往左对齐；</li><li>最后再考虑数值稳定性和内存风险。</li></ol><p>这个顺序比死记代码可靠。之后再遇到深度学习里的 batch、channel、embedding、logits、distance matrix，本质上还是在处理数组形状和维度变换。</p>]]></content>
      
      
